  • Konstruktordetails

    • Matrix

      public Matrix(double[][] elements, int columns, int rows)
      Constructor of custom Matrix class. Takes 2-dim double array of complex numbers to construct 3-dim matrix with size of columns * rows * 2.
      Parameter:
      elements - 2-dim double array
      columns - Integer number of matrix columns
      rows - Integer number of matrix rows
